---
title: Tangy Turkey Burgers with German-Style Potato Salad
description: Pan-fried, crispy, turkey goodness! This burger has all the toppings to take your meal to the next level with crunchy pickles and savoury caramelized onions. We've even chopped up some pickles to add zing to our classic potato salad. It's safe to say you won't miss BBQ with this stovetop-friendly dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-dinde-035cf548.jpg
